<td>
<p><b>Combatants:</b></p>
<ul>
<li><a href="/wiki/File:Coat_of_Arms_of_the_Russian_Federation.svg" class="image" title="Coat of Arms of the Russian Federation.svg"><img alt="" src="http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/f/f2/Coat_of_Arms_of_the_Russian_Federation.svg/20px-Coat_of_Arms_of_the_Russian_Federation.svg.png" width="20" height="24" border="0" /></a> <a href="/wiki/Russia" title="Russia">Russian Federation</a>
<ul>
