<li><a href="http://www.guardian.co.uk/gall/0,,1296787,00.html" class="external text" title="http://www.guardian.co.uk/gall/0,,1296787,00.html" rel="nofollow">In pictures. The Beslan School Siege</a>, <i><a href="/wiki/The_Guardian" title="The Guardian">The Guardian</a></i>, September 2004.</li>
<li><a href="http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/europe/3636196.stm" class="external text" title="http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/europe/3636196.stm" rel="nofollow">Russian TV broadcasts siege video</a> <a href="/wiki/British_Broadcasting_Corporation" title="British Broadcasting Corporation" class="mw-redirect">BBC News</a>, September 7, 2004.</li>
<li><a href="http://www.utro.ru/gallery.shtml?20040903storm,1,147,,240" class="external text" title="http://www.utro.ru/gallery.shtml?20040903storm,1,147,,240" rel="nofollow">List of screen shots from BBC News &amp; CNN</a>.</li>
<li><a href="http://news.bbc.co.uk/media/avdb/news_web/video/9012da6800246e0/nb/09012da6800248fc_16x9_nb.asx" class="external text" title="http://news.bbc.co.uk/media/avdb/news_web/video/9012da6800246e0/nb/09012da6800248fc_16x9_nb.asx" rel="nofollow">Beslan. To remember school siege victims</a>, <a href="/wiki/British_Broadcasting_Corporation" title="British Broadcasting Corporation" class="mw-redirect">BBC News</a>.</li>
<li><a href="http://www.online-translator.com/url/tran_url.asp?lang=en&amp;direction=re&amp;autotranslate=on&amp;transliterate=on&amp;url=http%3A%2F%2Fnewizv.ru%2Ffotoreport%2F%3Ff_id=11" class="external text" title="http://www.online-translator.com/url/tran_url.asp?lang=en&amp;direction=re&amp;autotranslate=on&amp;transliterate=on&amp;url=http%3A%2F%2Fnewizv.ru%2Ffotoreport%2F%3Ff_id=11" rel="nofollow">Missing hostages' photos</a>", <i><a href="/wiki/Novye_Izvestia" title="Novye Izvestia" class="mw-redirect">Novye Izvestia</a></i>. Machine-translated by www.online-translator.com.</li>
<li><a href="http://video.google.com/videoplay?docid=-4027837866779837178" class="external text" title="http://video.google.com/videoplay?docid=-4027837866779837178" rel="nofollow">Dispatches: Beslan</a>, a <a href="/wiki/Channel_4" title="Channel 4">Channel 4</a> documentary with interviews of people directly involved and affected by the siege.</li>
<li><a href="http://news.yahoo.com/page/interactives/hotzone/photoessay?f=chechnya/20060301pe_chechnya" class="external text" title="http://news.yahoo.com/page/interactives/hotzone/photoessay?f=chechnya/20060301pe_chechnya" rel="nofollow">Life after Beslan</a>. <a href="/wiki/Kevin_Sites" title="Kevin Sites">Kevin Sites</a> photo essay (15 images).</li>
