<li><a href="http://www.golosbeslana.ru/pamyat.htm" class="external text" title="http://www.golosbeslana.ru/pamyat.htm" rel="nofollow">Pictures of children, teachers and parents who were killed during the event</a>.</li>
<li><a href="http://terror.fredogfrihed.dk/Beslan%20-%20September%201-3%202004/Beslan.htm" class="external text" title="http://terror.fredogfrihed.dk/Beslan%20-%20September%201-3%202004/Beslan.htm" rel="nofollow">Portraits of the killed hostages</a>.</li>
